description: Data (values) are divided into time segmets. First key is `year`, second key is `month` of the year, third key is `day` of the month and fourth key is `hour` of the day. Every day is array of 6 values for every 10th minute starting at 0 and ending at 50 -> so value at data[`values`][`23`][`02`][`05`][`10`][2] coresponds to value captured 5th February of 2023 in 10:20.
